The target image shows a structure resembling a small vehicle. It has 6 blocks in total, arranged in 3 layers.  The base layer consists of two identical orange cylindrical blocks. The second layer has a yellow rectangular block sitting on top of each of the cylindrical blocks.  The third layer comprises a blue cube positioned above the yellow block on the right side, and a red cube positioned above the yellow block on the left.
